-Selectionner une image:
Intent i2=new Intent();
        i2.setType("image/*");
        i2.setAction(Intent.ACTION_GET_CONTENT);
        startActivityForResult(i2,2);

___________________________________
pdf:

Intent i2=new Intent();
        i2.setType("application/pdf");
        i2.setAction(Intent.ACTION_GET_CONTENT);
        startActivityForResult(i2,2);


